{My Dad} gets up at 4 a.m. to do the milking. {My Mum}gets up at 6.30 to make our breakfast. {Alison and I}get washed and dressed and catch the school minibus at 8.10.{My Mum}goes to her work at the butcher's in{Portsoy} at 8.35.
{My oldest sister}works in the Spar at{ {Banff, another }in the Old Folk's Home in {Keith} and {the third}at the Golf Club in {Banff.}
{My Dad}comes home from 9 till 12.50 then goes back to the farm till 6.30.{ {My Mum}finishes work at 1. {Alison and {I}come home at 4.05. We have tea at 5.30 then play or watch t.v. till 9 o clock. Then we have our coffee and go to bed. My name is Denise.
